                                <p>S·ª± th√†nh c√¥ng l√¢u d√†i c·ªßa 5S ph·ª• thu·ªôc r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu v√†o s·ª± cam k·∫øt t·ª´ c·∫•p qu·∫£n l√Ω. L√£nh ƒë·∫°o c·∫ßn ph·∫£i l√†m g∆∞∆°ng v√† th∆∞·ªùng xuy√™n nh·∫•n m·∫°nh t·∫ßm quan tr·ªçng c·ªßa k·ª∑ lu·∫≠t k·ªπ thu·∫≠t s·ªë.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section id="office-2-0" class="content-section">
                    <div class="text-center mb-10">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 font-condensed">OFFICE 2.0 x 5S ONLINE üè¢</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-slate-500">T·ª´ Kh√¥ng Gian V·∫≠t L√Ω ƒë·∫øn K·ª∑ Lu·∫≠t S·ªë</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 text-center mb-8">
                        <p class="italic text-slate-600">S√°ng ki·∫øn Office 2.0 l√† s·ª± th·ªÉ hi·ªán ho√†n h·∫£o c·ªßa 5S trong m√¥i tr∆∞·ªùng l√†m vi·ªác v·∫≠t l√Ω. 5S Online m·ªü r·ªông nh·ªØng nguy√™n t·∫Øc n√†y v√†o kh√¥ng gian k·ªπ thu·∫≠t s·ªë c·ªßa ch√∫ng ta, t·∫°o ra m·ªôt h·ªá sinh th√°i l√†m vi·ªác hi·ªáu qu·∫£ v√† g·ªçn g√†ng to√†n di·ªán.</p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg mt-4">
                        <table>
                            <thead>
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="w-1/3">Nguy√™n t·∫Øc Office 2.0</th>
