                                <tr>
                                    <td><strong>"Kh√¥ng ƒë·ªì linh tinh, kh√¥ng ƒë·ªì c√° nh√¢n"</strong> tr√™n b√†n l√†m vi·ªác.</td>
                                    <td><strong>S1 - S√†ng l·ªçc (Seiri):</strong> Lo·∫°i b·ªè nh·ªØng th·ª© kh√¥ng c·∫ßn thi·∫øt.</td>
                                    <td>X√≥a email v√† t·ªáp tin r√°c. √Åp d·ª•ng quy t·∫Øc 4D (Delete, Do, Delegate, Defer) ƒë·ªÉ gi·ªØ h·ªôp th∆∞ ƒë·∫øn s·∫°ch s·∫Ω.</td>
