                                    <td>X√¢y d·ª±ng c·∫•u tr√∫c th∆∞ m·ª•c logic tr√™n OneDrive/SharePoint. S·ª≠ d·ª•ng Categories v√† Folders trong Outlook ƒë·ªÉ ph√¢n lo·∫°i email.</td>
